Description:
    Creates a default AngularJS app

Example:
    yo pongstr

    This will create:
      .editorconfig
      .eslintrc
      .gitignore

      gulpfile.js
      bower.json
      package.json

      src/app/
      src/app/index.js
      src/app/index.html

      src/scss/
      src/scss/bootstrap (symlink)
      src/scss/bourbon   (symlink)
      src/scss/_variables.scss
      src/scss/_bootstrap.scss
      src/scss/styles.scss
